text: Yue Safy (born 8 November 2000) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for Phnom Penh Crown in the Cambodian League and the Cambodia U-23. ==Club career== Yue Safy made his senior debut in Cambodia League on 16 March 2018 for Phnom Penh Crown. ==International career== Yue Safy made his senior debut in 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification against Australia national under-23 soccer team on 22 March 2019. == External links == *Yue Safy at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:2000 births Category:Cambodian footballers Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
